!.vscode/mcp.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

# ── Claude Code local config (onboarding lives in CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md) ─
.claude/

# Local agent memory / workbook
AGENT_WORKBOOK.md

aieng-ui/frontend/package-lock.json
refer/*